data.description: Location! Location! Location! Like-new construction in the McMinnville Country Club neighborhood. Located in the coveted subdivision "The Links" with no HOA. The McMinnville Country Club features an 18 hole golf course, full bar and restaurant, new community in ground pool, tennis court, and playground - all just a 5 minute walk away. The 1200 sq ft unfinished second level gives this home massive potential for a large growing family or some sweat equity... or both! A full price offer before 12/25/2023 could include a golf cart!! This property is priced to sell - two great comps nearby have sold for 425k and 430k, neither of which are located in this wonderful neighborhood, have a 1200 sq ft unfinished second level, or privacy fence! Act fast, I expect this to move quickly!
